521
00:42:17,451 --> 00:42:18,786
After she left for the US,

522
00:42:19,370 --> 00:42:20,871
she stopped talking to me.

523
00:42:22,122 --> 00:42:25,793
Her mother suddenly disappeared
one day too.

524
00:42:26,627 --> 00:42:29,004
Nobody knew what happened to those two.

525
00:42:30,422 --> 00:42:34,051
She disappeared without a trace,

526
00:42:37,304 --> 00:42:38,430
