528
00:43:29,064 --> 00:43:29,898
La-el.

529
00:43:37,865 --> 00:43:38,782
I'm sorry.

530
00:43:40,576 --> 00:43:41,577
Dad…

531
00:43:42,620 --> 00:43:44,580
I have to do this to protect my company

532
00:43:45,414 --> 00:43:48,167
