-Honey!
-Dad!

535
00:43:58,385 --> 00:43:59,261
Honey!

536
00:43:59,928 --> 00:44:03,015
Who are you? Why are you doing this?

537
00:44:03,098 --> 00:44:04,516
-Honey!
-Dad!

538
00:44:07,311 --> 00:44:10,648
Hey, Lee Tae-joon.
This isn't rocket science.

539
00:44:10,731 --> 00:44:13,359
"I became a corporate spy
to get more money."

540
00:44:13,442 --> 00:44:15,402
"I'm sorry for handing over
that technology."

541
00:44:15,486 --> 00:44:18,238
"This will never happen again."

542
00:44:18,322 --> 00:44:20,699
Just sign it, and we'll let you go.

543
00:44:22,242 --> 00:44:23,202
I promise.

544
00:44:23,911 --> 00:44:27,331
That never happened.

545
00:44:28,457 --> 00:44:31,502
That's not true…

546
00:44:35,047 --> 00:44:35,881
Why you…

547
00:44:37,883 --> 00:44:38,884
Dad!

548
00:44:39,385 --> 00:44:40,511
Hey.

549
00:44:40,594 --> 00:44:43,180
You idiot. It's not that hard.

550
00:44:43,263 --> 00:44:45,182
-Dad!
-Just sign.

551
00:44:45,265 --> 00:44:47,184
It's just one signature, you idiot.

552
00:44:47,267 --> 00:44:50,396
Is it that hard? Just sign it, you idiot!

553
00:44:50,479 --> 00:44:52,356
-Please don't do this!
-He's bleeding.

554
00:44:52,439 --> 00:44:53,440
-Please don't hurt him.
-Please don't do this.

555
00:44:53,524 --> 00:44:54,525
Gosh, they're so loud.

556
00:44:56,276 --> 00:44:58,529
If you're not going to convince him
to admit his fault, get out.

557
00:44:58,612 --> 00:45:00,280
This is the end of your damn visit.

558
00:45:00,364 --> 00:45:03,117
-What are you doing? No! Honey!
-No! Dad!

559
00:45:03,200 --> 00:45:04,368
Honey!

560
00:45:05,327 --> 00:45:07,538
Damn, you're made of tougher shit
than I thought.

561
00:45:07,621 --> 00:45:08,455
Mom.

562
00:45:08,956 --> 00:45:12,167
Hey, is it really so damn hard
to just draw a signature?

563
00:45:12,793 --> 00:45:13,669
Mom…

564
00:45:15,045 --> 00:45:15,879
Mom…

565
00:45:17,714 --> 00:45:20,384
Back in the day,
he'd be spilling the truth right now.

566
00:45:23,804 --> 00:45:25,389
This world has gotten
so much easier to live in.

567
00:45:25,931 --> 00:45:27,015
Goddammit.

568
00:45:27,099 --> 00:45:30,644
This is taking so long
because I'm trying to be nice.

569
00:45:30,727 --> 00:45:32,271
Now that you've got him,

570
00:45:32,354 --> 00:45:34,022
he'll confess in no time, sir.

571
00:45:34,106 --> 00:45:35,691
In no time, my ass.

572
00:45:35,774 --> 00:45:38,318
The higher-ups won't let me do it.

573
00:45:43,699 --> 00:45:44,700
Hey.

574
00:45:45,742 --> 00:45:46,785
Just leave her.

575
00:46:06,680 --> 00:46:07,973
I can't eat this anymore.

576
00:46:08,056 --> 00:46:09,057
This is choking me up.

577
00:46:16,899 --> 00:46:18,108
All right, give that here.

578
00:46:18,901 --> 00:46:21,111
Okay, let's do this, like that.

579
00:46:30,787 --> 00:46:32,331
Who the hell do you think you are?

580
00:46:33,248 --> 00:46:34,082
Sir!

581
00:46:34,166 --> 00:46:36,460
Why, you little…

582
00:46:38,837 --> 00:46:39,922
Hey.

583
00:46:40,714 --> 00:46:41,548
Move aside.

584
00:46:49,056 --> 00:46:50,224
Damn, you little brat.

585
00:46:50,307 --> 00:46:52,267
You've got some spirit in you,
haven't you?

586
00:46:52,976 --> 00:46:55,145
You've been glaring at me all this time.

587
00:46:55,229 --> 00:46:56,063
The entire time.

588
00:46:57,022 --> 00:46:58,857
So what are you going to do now?

589
00:46:58,941 --> 00:47:00,776
What are you going to do?

590
00:47:00,859 --> 00:47:01,693
Hey.

591
00:47:03,654 --> 00:47:05,614
If your dad doesn't sign it,

592
00:47:06,156 --> 00:47:07,866
he's going to die.

593
00:47:09,076 --> 00:47:10,494
You see him right there?

594
00:47:10,577 --> 00:47:11,828
Lying on the ground?

595
00:47:16,708 --> 00:47:18,293
You little brat.

596
00:47:29,555 --> 00:47:31,598
-Dad.
-Honey!

597
00:47:31,682 --> 00:47:32,766
Dad.

598
00:47:36,895 --> 00:47:38,230
Honey!

599
00:47:38,313 --> 00:47:39,690
Dad.

600
00:47:40,857 --> 00:47:42,317
Honey!

601
00:47:42,901 --> 00:47:43,819
Mom!

602
00:47:43,902 --> 00:47:45,487
-Mom!
-What are you doing?

603
00:47:45,571 --> 00:47:46,697
Get her out of here.

604
00:47:47,281 --> 00:47:48,407
No!

605
00:47:50,617 --> 00:47:51,451
Mom!

606
00:47:56,540 --> 00:47:57,374
LEE TAE-JOON
CAUSE OF DEATH: STRANGULATION

607
00:47:57,457 --> 00:47:59,251
Cremate him right away,

608
00:47:59,334 --> 00:48:01,878
and don't allow any family interviews.

609
00:48:01,962 --> 00:48:03,046
Yes, sir.

610
00:48:18,270 --> 00:48:20,522
If your dad doesn't sign it,

611
00:48:21,106 --> 00:48:22,816
he's going to die.

612
00:49:00,103 --> 00:49:02,272
I've gotten rid of Lee Tae-joon.

613
00:49:03,690 --> 00:49:06,735
LY and GEDIKS are all yours now.

614
00:49:16,620 --> 00:49:19,247
MEETING BETWEEN VARIOUS MINISTRIES
AND FINANCIAL INDUSTRIES

615
00:49:40,102 --> 00:49:43,772
Today, we're interviewing
Prime Minister Han and Ms. Han So-ra.

616
00:49:44,940 --> 00:49:46,358
Prime Minister Han.

617
00:49:46,858 --> 00:49:50,987
Thank you for being at this charity event
to help kids with incurable diseases.

618
00:49:51,071 --> 00:49:53,865
I see that your daughter, Ms. Han So-ra,
is here as well.

619
00:49:53,949 --> 00:49:55,867
I'm here to make sure that people know

620
00:49:55,951 --> 00:49:58,829
that this pretty young lady
is my daughter,

621
00:49:58,912 --> 00:50:00,455
since a lot of people
don't seem to know that.

622
00:50:35,407 --> 00:50:36,241
Excuse me.

623
00:50:41,371 --> 00:50:43,373
I didn't know his daughter was home.

624
00:50:43,874 --> 00:50:45,625
Isn't your mother at the hospital?

625
00:50:45,709 --> 00:50:47,210
I thought you'd be with her.

626
00:50:47,711 --> 00:50:48,754
What do you think you're doing?

627
00:50:49,296 --> 00:50:51,214
Well, we're just…

628
00:50:56,762 --> 00:50:58,054
Find Mr. Lee's seal first.

629
00:50:58,138 --> 00:50:59,389
We can get the
daughter's statement tomorrow…

630
00:51:04,352 --> 00:51:05,187
Director.

631
00:51:10,358 --> 00:51:11,526
What are you doing here?

632
00:51:15,739 --> 00:51:16,865
La-el. We…

633
00:51:18,742 --> 00:51:19,743
Well…

634
00:51:25,415 --> 00:51:27,000
Hold on.

635
00:51:27,083 --> 00:51:28,251
I just need a moment.

636
00:51:28,335 --> 00:51:30,045
Hey! I just need…

637
00:51:44,518 --> 00:51:45,352
Go and look.

638
00:52:38,488 --> 00:52:39,865
You know Han So-ra, right?

639
00:52:39,948 --> 00:52:41,616
She's in our class too.

640
00:52:44,244 --> 00:52:45,620
Does Ms. Han

641
00:52:46,121 --> 00:52:48,248
not like to mingle with other people?

642
00:53:59,569 --> 00:54:00,403
Honey.

643
00:54:02,781 --> 00:54:04,282
You want to… Here?

644
00:54:05,700 --> 00:54:07,243
I can't help myself.

645
00:54:08,036 --> 00:54:09,663
Dancing to the tango made me feel so hot.

646
00:54:10,914 --> 00:54:11,748
Babe.

647
00:54:11,831 --> 00:54:14,876
You know that I want you
and that I've been waiting for this.

648
00:54:14,960 --> 00:54:16,211
But can we do this at home?

649
00:54:16,294 --> 00:54:17,796
I don't want somebody to find us.

650
00:54:23,218 --> 00:54:24,469
WAITING ROOM FOR FEMALE PERFORMERS

651
00:55:41,671 --> 00:55:42,756
I love you, honey.

652
00:56:07,238 --> 00:56:08,364
Did you have fun, Da-bi?

653
00:56:09,866 --> 00:56:12,285
Mom, I made a new friend.

654
00:56:12,368 --> 00:56:13,203
Did you, now?

655
00:56:28,635 --> 00:56:30,595
Da-bi, do you want something to eat?

656
00:56:31,346 --> 00:56:32,472
Do you want this?

657
00:56:56,412 --> 00:56:58,748
You all live up in a castle in the clouds.

658
00:57:02,627 --> 00:57:04,337
You're still too far to reach,

659
00:57:06,005 --> 00:57:07,674
but the key to the shortcut there

660
00:57:10,260 --> 00:57:11,427
lies in your heart.

661
00:57:17,851 --> 00:57:19,352
When I have it in my hands,

662
00:57:21,271 --> 00:57:22,897
I'll drag all of you with me

663
00:57:24,649 --> 00:57:26,818
into the hellfire that burned my soul.

664
00:58:04,063 --> 00:58:05,857
Because I'm going to pay them back

665
00:58:05,940 --> 00:58:06,816
tenfold.

666
00:58:06,900 --> 00:58:08,776
I wonder what she's trying to do.

667
00:58:10,945 --> 00:58:13,323
Would you mind helping me with something?

668
00:58:16,784 --> 00:58:17,785
Honey.

669
00:58:17,869 --> 00:58:22,081
Let's just take three days
to find out who Mr. Kang knows.

670
00:58:23,416 --> 00:58:24,459
Do you recognize me?

671
00:58:24,959 --> 00:58:26,044
Because I recognize you,

672
00:58:26,127 --> 00:58:26,961
Lee La-el.

673
00:58:27,837 --> 00:58:29,631
I didn't ask for your opinion.

674
00:58:29,714 --> 00:58:33,051
She doesn't know her place.
I'll just get rid of her.

675
00:58:33,551 --> 00:58:34,385
The bandoneon.

676
00:58:34,928 --> 00:58:36,596
Do you know how to play it?

677
00:58:37,096 --> 00:58:37,972
Where's Yoon-gyeom?

678
00:58:38,056 --> 00:58:40,266
You're supposed to listen
to your partner's heart

679
00:58:40,350 --> 00:58:42,644
and become one with them
when you dance to a tango.

680
00:58:42,727 --> 00:58:43,853
With all your attention only on me.

681
00:58:44,896 --> 00:58:45,980
May I help you with that?

